get.description:
Provides more info about each model in /models

Parameters:
    regolo_model_id: Optional[str] = None

    - When regolo_model_id is passed, it will return the info for that specific model
    - When regolo_model_id is not passed, it will return the info for all models

Returns:
    Returns a dictionary containing information about each model.

Example Response:
```json
{
    "data": [
                {
                    "model_name": "fake-openai-endpoint",
                    "litellm_params": {
                        "api_base": "https://exampleopenaiendpoint-production.up.railway.app/",
                        "model": "openai/fake"
                    },
                    "model_info": {
                        "id": "112f74fab24a7a5245d2ced3536dd8f5f9192c57ee6e332af0f0512e08bed5af",
                        "db_model": false
                    }
                }
            ]
}

```

